{"tid":639623,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[有show 既撚樣入一入黎] gillette 終於良心發現 (我諗係掛)","createTime":"2018-04-23T15:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T15:29:16.000Z","uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eb32f6a18c6ddaa29a8503e38530fbfc5879c78c","tid":639623,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的， gillette 啲刀頭不褸好鳩鬼貴， 雖然有啲代用頭 ， 但係好撚鳩垃圾， 所以阿叔我晨咁撚早就轉左用safety razor 喇。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230132_8925b09bdcc54ff66a6b9a54d82eb298.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230132_8925b09bdcc54ff66a6b9a54d82eb298.png&h=0b63aee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（巳經無做電視， 但個名仲有電視兩個字既網店， 阿叔成兩年無買gillette 刀頭 ， 唔知價）<br />\n<br />\n不過我近排見amazon 上高， gillette 出左條新line ， 啲刀頭似符幾抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 所以post 比大家睇下：<br />\n<br />\nmatch 3 （ 我諗係掛）： 對返港紙， 大約 50 雞 8 個 ， 不過阿叔未買過<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230022_aaa251c7eab1b1461cfd8a02f4f2e5f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230022_aaa251c7eab1b1461cfd8a02f4f2e5f8.png&h=44833640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Gillette-Razor-Blade-Refills-Count/dp/B07751QCHD/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=beauty&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1523495252&amp;sr=1-2&amp;keywords=gillette+3&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=mansshablo-20&amp;linkId=ab9ef5cd128af4d290094c555a86850e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGillette-Razor-Blade-Refills-Count%2Fdp%2FB07751QCHD%2Fref%3Das_li_ss_tl%3Fs%3Dbeauty%26ie%3DUTF8%26qid%3D1523495252%26sr%3D1-2%26keywords%3Dgillette%2B3%26linkCode%3Dsl1%26tag%3Dmansshablo-20%26linkId%3Dab9ef5cd128af4d290094c555a86850e&d=gOcxULt2WpiTOBrJDZ%2FA0qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8b32b548\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Gillette-Razor-Blade-Refills-Count/dp/B07751QCHD/ref=as_li_ss_tl?s=beauty&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1523495252&amp;sr=1-2&amp;keywords=gillette+3&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=mansshablo-20&amp;linkId=ab9ef5cd128af4d290094c555a86850e</a><br />\n<br />\n對手， personna 出既代用頭 easyfit 3 （20 蚊美金十五個，阿叔上次去旅行買定， 巳經比左細佬用）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/230419_c73d03988daff55a590886e64adbd56c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F230419_c73d03988daff55a590886e64adbd56c.png&h=280c408b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\npersonna 係大廠黎， 同gillette 一路都係競爭對手， 由20 世紀頭玩到而家， personna仲有出手術刀片。  <br />\n<br />\n不過見到個價都知巳經輸左， 更加唔洗講佢上高果個蘆薈gel 一路剃 一路溶，搞到塊面滑珊珊 ，  剃到阿叔好唔適服<br />\n<br />\n同以前用gillette 啲 刀頭 比輸晒<br />\n<br />\n5 刀頭 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/231135_c2cdccf2a528bbebe6fef65e00885b56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F231135_c2cdccf2a528bbebe6fef65e00885b56.png&h=c094e0e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Gillette-Razor-Blade-Refills-Count/dp/B0774SWZH2/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1523314974&amp;sr=8-4&amp;keywords=gillette+5&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=mansshablo-20&amp;linkId=5fb79b88eb93fd052dd29ff244501ca5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FGillette-Razor-Blade-Refills-Count%2Fdp%2FB0774SWZH2%2Fref%3Das_li_ss_tl%3Fie%3DUTF8%26qid%3D1523314974%26sr%3D8-4%26keywords%3Dgillette%2B5%26linkCode%3Dsl1%26tag%3Dmansshablo-20%26linkId%3D5fb79b88eb93fd052dd29ff244501ca5&d=gOcxULt2WpiTOBrJDZ%2FA0qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f4be1506\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Gillette-Razor-Blade-Refills-Count/dp/B0774SWZH2/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1523314974&amp;sr=8-4&amp;keywords=gillette+5&amp;linkCode=sl1&amp;tag=mansshablo-20&amp;linkId=5fb79b88eb93fd052dd29ff244501ca5</a><br />\n對手， personna 出既代用頭 easyfit 5 （30 蚊美金十二個）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/231625_fb71b421192bce0d8099f342592dbf96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F231625_fb71b421192bce0d8099f342592dbf96.png&h=f2c0d88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Personna-EasyFit-Fusion-Compatible-Cartridges/dp/B07BB1W6G8/ref=sr_1_1_s_it?s=beauty&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1524496489&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=easyfit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPersonna-EasyFit-Fusion-Compatible-Cartridges%2Fdp%2FB07BB1W6G8%2Fref%3Dsr_1_1_s_it%3Fs%3Dbeauty%26ie%3DUTF8%26qid%3D1524496489%26sr%3D1-1%26keywords%3Deasyfit&d=gOcxULt2WpiTOBrJDZ%2FA0qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=bd8bee21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Personna-EasyFit-Fusion-Compatible-Cartridges/dp/B07BB1W6G8/ref=sr_1_1_s_it?s=beauty&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1524496489&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=easyfit</a><br />\n見到三刀頭巳經咁様， 五刀頭唔撚洗講啦， 30蚊美金先得十二粒， 貴鳩到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 （30蚊美金夠阿叔買到三百塊astra 刀片， 剃到起碼六年）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/232203_4dfb64263612f5df6ad5bfd17a168942.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F232203_4dfb64263612f5df6ad5bfd17a168942.png&h=9ad3d6d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過近排美金貴， 建議大家都係bookmark 先， 等到下次集運一炮過買返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5a45fcc28abdcce83d9c7d317f5ab36e0d8e9d","tid":639623,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T15:29:16.000Z","msg":"屌， 一出完post ， gillette 3 就加左價， gillette 正仆街 黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}